<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;h2&gt;Total Cost of Your Trademark Filing&lt;/h2&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;div class="cost" id="totalCost"&gt;$0.00&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;!-- Slider directly under total --&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;input type="range" id="classes" min="1" max="10" value="1" step="1"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;div class="class-label"&gt;&lt;span id="classLabel"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; Class(es)&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;small&gt;Move the slider to change the number of Classes you plan to include in your trademark application.&lt;/small&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;p style="margin-top:25px;"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>Cost is calculated based on the number of Classes you select and it includes our fee (excl. taxes).</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;!-- RIGHT: About section --&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;div class="right"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;h2&gt;More About Classes&lt;/h2&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>When you apply for a trademark, you need to list the products or services your trademark will cover, which are organized into “Classes”.</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>Each additional class adds CA$145.12 in government fees. You can read more about Classes<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;a href="https://clearviewcounsel.io/our-blog/understanding-trademark-classes-in-canada" target="_blank"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">&lt;script&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>const baseFee = 799;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>const firstClassFee = 478.15;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>const addClassFee = 145.12;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>const classesInput = document.getElementById('classes');</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>const classLabel = document.getElementById('classLabel');</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>const totalCost = document.getElementById('totalCost');</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>function updateCost() {</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>const classes = parseInt(classesInput.value, 10);</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>classLabel.textContent = classes;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>let cost = baseFee + firstClassFee;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>if (classes &gt; 1) {</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>cost += (classes - 1) * addClassFee;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>}</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>totalCost.textContent = "CA$" + cost.toLocaleString(undefined, {minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2});</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>}</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>classesInput.addEventListener('input', updateCost);</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>updateCost(); // initialize</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;/script&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
